Step-6 Load all the Dimension Tables using Merge Statement 6


Run the code file to load the data into Dim_Availability, Dim_BookingAgent, and Dim_Property Table



1) This part of the script will load the data into De-normalized Dim_Availability Table using SCD Type-1.



2) This part of the script will load the data into De-normalized Dim_BookingAgent Table using SCD Type-1.



3) This part of the script will load the data into De-normalized Dim_Property Table, it will be added to the Dim_Property using SCD Type-1.


We can see the data into the tables.



To load these tables, We have used Slowly Changing Dimension Type-I.  Meaning when we update the Data Mart,  a new record will be added and the existing records will get updated.

Following the link we see how to load data using merge statement in  SQL.

https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/merge-statement-sql-explained/
